	<td bgcolor='#FBFBFB' valign='top' width='100%' bordercolor='#FBFBFB'>
	<table width='100%' border='0' cellspacing='0' cellpadding='3'><tr><td><font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" size="2" ><img src="http://www.eqinterface.com/images/sections/eqpatch.gif" align="right"><font color="darkred"><b>Scheduled Update for all EverQuest Servers</b></font><br />
<font color="darkblue">On Thursday, October 9th, at 3:00 am PDT (-7 hours UTC), all EverQuest servers will be brought down for an update. The estimated down time is 5 hours.</font><br />
